sourcesContent:
let container = {
  width: "100%",
  // height: "85%"
}

let searchInput = {
  width: "100%",
  minWidth: "1000px",
  height: "30px",
  outlineWidth: "0px",
  boxSizing: "border-box",
  fontSize: "17px",
  margin: "0 0 10px 10px"
}

let listContainer = {
  minWidth: "100%",
  height: "100%",
  overflowY: "scroll",
  overflowX: "hidden",
  marginLeft: "10px"
}

let profileListContainer = {
  display: "flex",
  height: "22px",
  width: "100%",
  marginBottom: "3px",
  border: "1px solid #4382BC",
  borderRadius: "5px 0px 0px 5px",
  backgroundColor: "#e8fefd",
  cursor: "default",
}

let profileListDataMain = {
  cursor: "pointer",
  fontSize: "15px",
  textAlign: "center",
  minWidth: "200px",
  color: "white",
  backgroundColor: "#4382BC",
  overflow: "hidden",
  whiteSpace: "nowrap",
  lineHeight: "22px",
  borderRadius: "4px 0px 0px 4px",
}

let profileListDataOther = {
  cursor: "default",
  fontSize: "15px",
  textAlign: "center",
  width: "16.67%",
  textTransform: "capitalize",
  overflow: "hidden",
  whiteSpace: "nowrap",
  textOverflow: "ellipsis",
  lineHeight: "20px",
}

export {
  container,
  searchInput,
  listContainer,
  profileListContainer,
  profileListDataMain,
  profileListDataOther
}
